    ('刷卡', 'shuākǎ', 'quẹt thẻ', '超市支持刷卡付款，非常方便。', 'Chāoshì zhīchí shuākǎ fùkuǎn, fēicháng fāngbiàn.', 'Siêu thị hỗ trợ quẹt thẻ thanh toán, rất tiện lợi.', 'https://ssmqppvkgffknfqdvpwg.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/card-audio/templates/mua-sam-thanh-toan-150/word-3f156b4337578f8d8341fef8.mp3', 'https://ssmqppvkgffknfqdvpwg.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/card-audio/templates/mua-sam-thanh-toan-150/sentence-3714e668f4190ccdc1b38554.mp3', 38),
